WEBVTT

00:05.005 --> 00:07.708
NARRATOR: You've heard
of the placebo effect.

00:07.741 --> 00:10.111
But are you aware...

00:10.144 --> 00:13.247
of the nocebo effect?

00:13.281 --> 00:16.417
In which the human body has
a negative physical reaction

00:16.450 --> 00:17.851
to a suggested harm.

00:17.885 --> 00:20.321
This will make you vomit.

00:24.258 --> 00:25.526
This will make you vomit.

00:30.664 --> 00:32.200
This will make you vomit.

00:32.233 --> 00:33.701
NARRATOR:
Your mind has the power

00:33.734 --> 00:36.137
to create
its own physical reality.

00:36.170 --> 00:37.205
This will make you vomit.

00:54.922 --> 00:58.826
NARRATOR: Why do we yawn
when we see others yawn?

00:58.859 --> 01:01.195
-NARRATOR: Throughout history,

01:01.229 --> 01:03.397
-there have been incidents.

01:03.431 --> 01:07.168
-The Dancing Plague of 1518...

01:07.201 --> 01:09.503
the Tanganyika
laughter epidemic...

01:11.239 --> 01:13.507
...the Hindu milk miracle.

01:13.541 --> 01:14.775
MAN:
Hey...

01:19.046 --> 01:23.517
Some believe they're
a response to stress.

01:32.826 --> 01:34.094
-She is our daughter!
-She is my daughter!

01:34.128 --> 01:35.596
You didn't have her by yourself!

01:35.629 --> 01:37.131
WOMAN: I don't care anymore,
what you have to say!

01:37.165 --> 01:38.499
I'm done!

01:43.171 --> 01:46.640
NARRATOR: Psychologists call it
a conversion disorder.

01:49.877 --> 01:52.446
In that the body converts
a mental stress...

01:53.947 --> 01:55.749
...to a set
of physical symptoms.

01:55.783 --> 01:58.452
In this case, a tic, or spasm.

02:01.088 --> 02:03.157
And, like any disorder,

02:03.191 --> 02:06.594
it can be contagious.

02:08.061 --> 02:09.297
This kind
of collective behavior

02:09.330 --> 02:10.998
is not limited to human beings.

02:15.336 --> 02:18.105
What we know is that,
in certain communities,

02:18.138 --> 02:21.475
under specific circumstances,

02:21.509 --> 02:25.446
an involuntary physical symptom
developed by one person...

02:26.880 --> 02:28.849
...can become viral.

02:31.452 --> 02:33.287
