I'd say the contagion
locks people

28:24.370 --> 28:26.338
inside their own brains.

28:26.372 --> 28:29.141
Inside their own realities.

28:29.175 --> 28:31.878
Yeah, this is Ptonomy's maze.

28:31.911 --> 28:34.546
Yeah, but... gardening?

28:37.416 --> 28:39.651
It isn't gardening.

28:39.685 --> 28:43.489
It's that he doesn't
remember us. See?

28:43.522 --> 28:45.657
He forgets what he's doing
after every rose,

28:45.691 --> 28:48.327
and then the shears and
the basket-- they remind him.

28:48.360 --> 28:51.063
So what are you saying?

28:51.097 --> 28:52.598
It's a fantasy.

28:52.631 --> 28:56.903
Or... maybe I should say
a core desire.

28:56.936 --> 28:59.405
Our friend here
is a memory machine.

28:59.438 --> 29:01.040
He remembers every moment
of every day.

29:01.073 --> 29:03.209
Now, if that was your condition,

29:03.242 --> 29:06.178
what might you wish for?

29:06.212 --> 29:08.047
To forget.

29:08.080 --> 29:12.018
I mean, it's beautiful, really.

29:12.051 --> 29:15.922
To live in the moment--
no past, no future.

29:15.955 --> 29:17.656
DAVID:
Yeah, but it's not real.

29:17.689 --> 29:21.260
CARY: It's real to him.
In this moment.

29:21.293 --> 29:23.729
What are you saying,
we should leave him here?

29:23.762 --> 29:25.564
I'm not saying anything.

29:25.597 --> 29:27.099
I'm merely making
an observation.

29:27.133 --> 29:29.535
What if it was Kerry?

29:31.637 --> 29:33.806
You're right.
Wake him up.

29:39.578 --> 29:40.847
How?

29:40.880 --> 29:43.449
I don't know.
You're the psychic.

29:46.953 --> 29:48.120
Hello.

30:02.001 --> 30:03.569
What happened?

30:03.602 --> 30:05.838
You don't remember?

30:10.042 --> 30:11.277
No.

30:13.112 --> 30:15.814
-The monk got loose.
-Yeah.

30:15.848 --> 30:17.950
Everyone's infected.

30:17.984 --> 30:20.252
-No.

30:20.286 --> 30:22.121
He has the kids--
the monk--

30:22.154 --> 30:24.156
and they're armed,
but they're... kids, so...

30:24.190 --> 30:25.925
I

30:25.958 --> 30:28.527
-Uh, pied piper, humming,
it's a long story.
-Yeah.

30:40.606 --> 30:42.108
Cow.

30:42.141 --> 30:45.777
-No. I need to find Syd.

30:45.811 --> 30:48.380
-We should split up.
-We stay together.

30:48.414 --> 30:50.449
-PTONOMY: Definitely.

30:52.651 --> 30:55.854
-I'm fine. Let's go.

31:36.695 --> 31:38.530
Oh, no.

31:41.600 --> 31:44.570
Uh, no, it's not safe here
out in the open.

31:44.603 --> 31:47.106
We should get her to your lab.

31:47.139 --> 31:48.740
Yes.

31:48.774 --> 31:50.309
How?

32:08.560 --> 32:10.629
All right.

32:19.338 --> 32:20.406
Here goes.

32:24.176 --> 32:26.345
-PTONOMY: Yeah, hold on.

32:34.586 --> 32:36.122
Is this...

32:37.123 --> 32:38.657
Was mine like this?

32:38.690 --> 32:41.093
No. You were in a garden.

32:41.127 --> 32:42.694
In a sharp suit.

32:42.728 --> 32:45.097
-Yeah.
-Stay close.

33:02.548 --> 33:04.783
-I don't know.

33:04.816 --> 33:06.918
-Yes.

33:18.397 --> 33:20.366
-It's...
-We're...
-DAVID: A game.

33:20.399 --> 33:22.834
I don't have time for games.
Melanie!

33:30.776 --> 33:32.844
-Go through the door.

33:32.878 --> 33:35.081
No. Look around first.

33:37.683 --> 33:38.817
Look...

33:38.850 --> 33:40.919
around.

33:50.196 --> 33:52.464
-Climb... down.

34:00.272 --> 34:02.274
-Climb back up.
-Jump.

34:17.256 --> 34:19.358
Ow.

34:23.995 --> 34:25.797
DAVID:
Is this Melanie?

34:25.831 --> 34:27.233
Is she doing this?

34:27.266 --> 34:29.067
CARY:
I think so.

34:29.101 --> 34:32.738
-Perhaps her core desire

34:32.771 --> 34:34.306
is to be omnipotent.

34:34.340 --> 34:36.508
To control
the uncontrollable world

34:36.542 --> 34:38.410
from a distance, so she's...

34:39.445 --> 34:41.079
...everywhere.

34:43.048 --> 34:45.083
*

34:58.430 --> 35:00.499
:
The Minotaur.

35:02.301 --> 35:05.937
-Look... around.

35:19.318 --> 35:21.153
Melanie?

35:21.187 --> 35:23.489
It's David!

35:23.522 --> 35:25.524
You have to talk to me.

35:27.993 --> 35:30.396
The monk got free.
Everybody's infected.

35:30.429 --> 35:32.931
You're trapped inside your mind!

35:32.964 --> 35:35.167
If you come down here,

35:35.201 --> 35:38.237
we'll... we can go home.

35:39.271 --> 35:40.672
Okay?

35:41.907 --> 35:44.210
-I don't know.

36:00.692 --> 36:02.828
-Let's, uh...
-Yes.

36:07.165 --> 36:09.235
-That was...
-A Minotaur, yes.

36:09.268 --> 36:11.637
But why was it in a doggie
wheelchair? I don't know.

36:11.670 --> 36:12.838
Guys, we can't just...

36:12.871 --> 36:14.973
I don't have time for this.

36:44.336 --> 36:47.706
Melanie, please!

36:47.739 --> 36:49.741
They need our help!

36:59.318 --> 37:01.320
*

37:31.216 --> 37:33.218
*

38:06.151 --> 38:09.388
That was-that was nice,
but I think we need another...

38:20.932 --> 38:24.536
Should I... hug you?

38:24.570 --> 38:26.572
Please don't.

38:26.605 --> 38:28.874
Let's just go.

38:41.587 --> 38:44.255
Is that... a...

38:44.289 --> 38:45.891
A cow. Yes.

38:48.994 --> 38:51.296
-Okay, that really needs
to stop now.

38:51.329 --> 38:53.632
Nothing. It's...
I think Syd's in trouble.

38:53.665 --> 38:56.402
We need to split up now.
Cary and I will look for Syd.

38:56.435 --> 38:58.336
Melanie, you and Paul
find Fukyama.

38:58.370 --> 38:59.971
Oh, what if we see the monk?

39:00.005 --> 39:02.007
Ask him what he wants.
Just don't get too close.

39:02.040 --> 39:03.675
You should be immune now, but...

39:03.709 --> 39:05.977
-Yeah. I did a little thing
before we left.

39:06.011 --> 39:07.979
You did a thing in my head?

39:08.013 --> 39:09.515
DAVID:
Just don't get too close.

39:09.548 --> 39:10.616
What about the cow?

39:10.649 --> 39:12.283
Leave it here.

39:12.317 --> 39:14.285
I don't think I want a cow
in my lab.

39:14.319 --> 39:16.622
Guys, I don't care.
I got to find Syd.

39:16.655 --> 39:19.758
Let's check the pedestal first.

39:25.330 --> 39:28.033
Don't touch anything.

39:50.055 --> 39:52.057
Cary?

40:06.104 --> 40:07.939
*

40:19.384 --> 40:22.153
David? Oh...

40:22.187 --> 40:23.555
David.

43:55.934 --> 43:57.936
*

44:37.242 --> 44:39.644
CARY :
David?

44:42.013 --> 44:44.049
David?

44:56.661 --> 44:58.663
Oh, no!

45:05.003 --> 45:07.005
:
Oh, fudge!

45:35.033 --> 45:37.235
I'm sorry.

45:55.686 --> 45:57.688
*

46:21.679 --> 46:23.614
We want the weapon.

46:23.648 --> 46:25.783
What weapon?

46:25.817 --> 46:27.718
To kill the monster.

46:27.752 --> 46:30.922
They did not tell us he was
a monster and we took him in.

46:30.956 --> 46:32.891
PTONOMY:
There is no weapon.

46:32.924 --> 46:34.759
VERMILLION 1:
To Division 3 they told us.

46:34.792 --> 46:36.361
If there is a problem, go there.

46:36.394 --> 46:37.462
They will have the weapon.

46:40.598 --> 46:44.269
Will have. Do not have.

46:44.302 --> 46:46.737
A weapon was planned,
but never built.

46:46.771 --> 46:48.306
The body was buried.

46:48.339 --> 46:50.608
Then a new crisis and another.

46:50.641 --> 46:52.110
Over time we forgot.

46:52.143 --> 46:54.812
Do not believe.
Where is the weapon?

46:54.846 --> 46:56.781
Where's the body?

46:56.814 --> 46:58.816
VERMILLION 1:
No. We do not say.

46:58.850 --> 47:01.386
He is out there as well,
looking for it,

47:01.419 --> 47:03.154
the Shadow King.

47:03.188 --> 47:04.355
He must not find it.

47:04.389 --> 47:07.325
The end of everything.

47:09.360 --> 47:11.429
David.

47:11.462 --> 47:12.998
He's the weapon.

47:13.031 --> 47:15.166
VERMILLION 1:
The King is too powerful.

47:15.200 --> 47:18.103
His body, it will not drown.

47:18.136 --> 47:20.471
It does not burn.

47:20.505 --> 47:22.874
David can do it.

47:22.908 --> 47:24.442
Do what?

47:26.477 --> 47:28.779
Destroy the Shadow King.

47:28.813 --> 47:31.282
VERMILLION 1:
No. We do not want his help.

47:31.316 --> 47:33.318
He cannot be trusted.

47:33.351 --> 47:34.385
He works with the...

47:36.821 --> 47:39.690
MONK:
Teleportation.

47:39.724 --> 47:41.960
DAVID: Just-just quiet
for a second. Let me think.

47:41.993 --> 47:43.929
And stop making people sick.

47:43.962 --> 47:46.297
MONK:
People don't matter.

47:46.331 --> 47:47.798
Only the body matters.

47:47.832 --> 47:50.301
Well, they matter to me.

47:50.335 --> 47:51.702
They're my people.

47:51.736 --> 47:54.139
But you help him, the King.

47:54.172 --> 47:58.143
-And he will kill all of them.
-I am not...

47:58.176 --> 48:01.712
I have seen your mind...

48:01.746 --> 48:03.214
as you have mine.

48:17.028 --> 48:18.829
Where's the body?

48:18.863 --> 48:20.631
We're not afraid to die.

48:20.665 --> 48:23.368
Nobody is gonna...
Look...

48:23.401 --> 48:26.771
I'm having a really hard time
finding the landmarks here.

48:26.804 --> 48:28.506
Minds separated from bodies

48:28.539 --> 48:31.076
and Minotaurs in mazes.

48:31.109 --> 48:32.510
You got a girlfriend?

48:32.543 --> 48:34.445
-Yeah, I got one.

48:34.479 --> 48:35.913
Well, I-I got two, actually.

48:35.947 --> 48:38.249
Well, no, just one,
but in two time periods,

48:38.283 --> 48:40.185
which raises the question:
is it just one?

48:40.218 --> 48:43.254
Huh? I mean,
people change, right?

48:43.288 --> 48:45.923
We change,
so maybe she's different now.

48:45.957 --> 48:47.892
In the future.

48:47.925 --> 48:49.961
I don't...

48:49.995 --> 48:51.296
The point is, I love her-- them.

48:51.329 --> 48:54.632
And more importantly,
I trust her.

48:54.665 --> 48:56.467
And she told me things happen.

48:56.501 --> 48:57.868
Okay? In the future. Bad things.

48:57.902 --> 49:00.371
So I have to, I have to help.

49:00.405 --> 49:01.506
It's complicated.

49:01.539 --> 49:03.408
Look, just tell me where it is.

49:03.441 --> 49:04.742
The monastery.

49:04.775 --> 49:06.144
It was a valley
and now it's a desert.

49:06.177 --> 49:07.478
That much I know.

49:07.512 --> 49:10.048
Destroy it.

49:10.081 --> 49:11.549
I will.

49:11.582 --> 49:13.118
No, you won't.

49:13.151 --> 49:15.353
I promise.

49:15.386 --> 49:18.089
Just tell me where it is.
I won't let anything bad happen.

49:18.123 --> 49:20.625
It already has.

49:38.643 --> 49:40.278
Syd!

49:42.280 --> 49:45.883
-Oh, no, no, no, no, no, no, no.

49:45.916 --> 49:47.918
Oh.

52:11.329 --> 52:12.830
MAN: Now I get it.
